org.usfirst.frc.team449.robot.drive.unidirectional

Interface DriveUnidirectional

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DriveSubsystem, Updatable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DriveUnidirectionalSimple, DriveUnidirectionalWithGyro, DriveUnidirectionalWithGyroShiftable

    public interface DriveUnidirectional
extends DriveSubsystem, Updatable
    A drive with a left side and a right side. "Unidirectional" because it can only move forwards or backwards, not sideways.
